original_title: Crowd Lu 11th Anniversary Adult Live Tour
overview: To celebrate his 11th debut anniversary, Crowd Lu held his Adult Live Tour at the Taipei Arena for three consecutive days in April 2019. The singer-songwriter rearranged the melodies of some of his classic hits, and also performed popular tracks like "All I Have," "Adult," "You Complete Me," "He-R," "Trust Myself" and "Slow Soul" with his heart-melting voice.
title: Crowd Lu 11th Anniversary Adult Live Tour
